				\begin{document}$$P=max[0,min(1,\frac{{L}_{{\rm{ag}}}-{L}_{{\rm{low}}}}{{L}_{{\rm{up}}}-{L}_{{\rm{low}}}})]$$\end{document}P=max[0,min(1,Lag−LlowLup−Llow)]where L
